version_description:
【What's new】
· The synchronization system is fully upgraded to support pull-down refresh on the home page to manually synchronize data to the cloud;
· Cross-platform data security upgrades, user data is more solid;

【Bug fix】
· Fix the issue of missing authors of some books;
· Fixed the crash issue when importing WeChat reading notes in some cases.

Thank you for the use of Inkonote APP .
We have received feedbacks from all of you, and we will upgrade and iterate later. If you encounter problems or have great ideas in using app, please let us know through the feedback function in app.

